{"image_id": "PPL_2009_page_145", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "125", "bbox": [618.4, 1548.3, 655.0, 1571.4]}, {"text": "PPL", "bbox": [354.1, 104.9, 389.7, 123.3]}, {"text": "PPL Energy Supply", "bbox": [454.0, 104.9, 609.2, 123.3]}, {"text": "As of December 31,  As of December 31,", "bbox": [289.2, 124.7, 611.4, 143.5]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [313.8, 145.2, 351.4, 163.6]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [397.4, 145.2, 435.1, 163.6]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [479.3, 145.2, 517.0, 163.6]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [563.8, 145.2, 599.7, 163.6]}, {"text": "Long-Lived Assets", "bbox": [71.3, 165.1, 202.8, 183.5]}, {"text": "U.S.", "bbox": [93.8, 184.4, 127.6, 202.8]}, {"text": "$ 10,181  $ 9,762  $", "bbox": [287.1, 184.4, 472.1, 202.8]}, {"text": "6,676  $", "bbox": [488.5, 184.4, 550.4, 202.8]}, {"text": "6,433", "bbox": [572.8, 184.4, 610.4, 202.8]}, {"text": "U.K.", "bbox": [93.8, 203.5, 130.3, 221.9]}, {"text": "3,517", "bbox": [325.5, 203.5, 384.1, 221.9]}, {"text": "3,167", "bbox": [404.2, 203.5, 463.7, 221.9]}, {"text": "3,517", "bbox": [488.5, 203.5, 546.3, 221.9]}, {"text": "3,167", "bbox": [572.9, 203.5, 610.4, 221.9]}, {"text": "$ 13,698  $ 12,929  $ 10,193  $", "bbox": [287.0, 223.6, 550.4, 242.0]}, {"text": "9,600", "bbox": [572.9, 223.6, 610.5, 242.0]}, {"text": "(a)  Includes unrealized gains and losses from economic activity.  See Note 18", "bbox": [71.3, 266.9, 601.9, 285.3]}, {"text": "for additional information.", "bbox": [102.3, 286.0, 283.6, 304.4]}, {"text": "(b)  See \"PLR Contracts\" and \"NUG Purchases\" in Note 15 for a discussion of", "bbox": [71.3, 305.1, 601.4, 323.6]}, {"text": "the basis of accounting between reportable segments.", "bbox": [102.3, 324.3, 461.5, 342.7]}, {"text": "(c)  Includes interest income from affiliate(s).", "bbox": [71.3, 343.5, 383.5, 361.9]}, {"text": "(d)  Includes interest expense with affiliate.", "bbox": [71.3, 362.7, 367.8, 381.1]}, {"text": "(e)  Includes the results of Discontinued Operations of the Long Island", "bbox": [71.3, 381.8, 550.6, 400.2]}, {"text": "generation business and the majority of the Maine hydroelectric generation", "bbox": [102.3, 401.0, 606.9, 419.4]}, {"text": "business.  Also includes the loss on the sale of PPL Energy Supply's interest", "bbox": [102.3, 420.2, 614.2, 438.6]}, {"text": "in Wyman Unit 4.  See Note 9 for additional information.", "bbox": [102.3, 439.3, 489.6, 457.7]}, {"text": "(f)  Includes the results of Discontinued Operations of the Latin American", "bbox": [71.3, 458.5, 575.3, 477.0]}, {"text": "businesses.  See Note 9 for additional information.", "bbox": [102.3, 477.7, 444.0, 496.1]}, {"text": "(g)  Includes the results of Discontinued Operations of the natural gas and", "bbox": [71.3, 496.8, 571.3, 515.2]}, {"text": "propane businesses.  See Note 9 for additional information.", "bbox": [102.3, 516.0, 501.9, 534.5]}, {"text": "3. Variable Interest Entities", "bbox": [71.3, 559.4, 357.8, 582.7]}, {"text": "(PPL and PPL Energy Supply)", "bbox": [71.3, 607.4, 333.3, 630.5]}, {"text": "In December 2001, a subsidiary of PPL Energy Supply entered", "bbox": [71.3, 655.3, 602.1, 678.4]}, {"text": "into a $455 million operating lease arrangement, as lessee, for", "bbox": [71.3, 679.3, 593.3, 702.4]}, {"text": "the development, construction and operation of a gas-fired", "bbox": [71.3, 703.3, 563.6, 726.4]}, {"text": "combined-cycle generation facility located in Lower Mt. Bethel", "bbox": [71.3, 727.2, 607.9, 750.3]}, {"text": "Township, Northampton County, Pennsylvania.  This generation", "bbox": [71.3, 751.2, 615.4, 774.3]}, {"text": "facility has a total capacity (winter rating) of 624 MW at", "bbox": [71.3, 775.2, 549.0, 798.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009.  The owner/lessor of this generation", "bbox": [71.3, 799.1, 551.3, 822.2]}, {"text": "facility, LMB Funding, LP, was created to own/lease the facility", "bbox": [71.3, 823.1, 613.6, 846.2]}, {"text": "and incur the related financing costs.  The initial lease term", "bbox": [71.3, 847.0, 569.9, 870.1]}, {"text": "commenced on the date of commercial operation, which", "bbox": [71.3, 871.0, 545.4, 894.1]}, {"text": "occurred in May 2004, and ends in December 2013.  Under a", "bbox": [71.3, 895.0, 586.6, 918.1]}, {"text": "residual value guarantee, if the generation facility is sold at the", "bbox": [71.3, 918.9, 600.3, 942.0]}, {"text": "end of the lease term and the cash proceeds from the sale are less", "bbox": [71.3, 942.9, 619.0, 966.0]}, {"text": "than the original acquisition cost, the subsidiary of PPL Energy", "bbox": [71.3, 966.9, 604.7, 990.1]}, {"text": "Supply is obligated to pay up to 70.52% of the original", "bbox": [71.3, 990.8, 534.4, 1013.9]}, {"text": "acquisition cost.  This residual value guarantee protects the other", "bbox": [71.3, 1014.8, 617.0, 1038.0]}, {"text": "variable interest holders from losses related to their investments.", "bbox": [71.3, 1038.9, 619.6, 1062.0]}, {"text": "LMB Funding, LP cannot extend or cancel the lease or sell the", "bbox": [71.3, 1062.7, 598.7, 1085.9]}, {"text": "facility without the prior consent of the PPL Energy Supply", "bbox": [71.3, 1086.8, 573.8, 1109.9]}, {"text": "subsidiary.  As a result, LMB Funding, LP was determined to be", "bbox": [71.3, 1110.8, 614.8, 1133.9]}, {"text": "a variable interest entity and the subsidiary of PPL Energy", "bbox": [71.3, 1134.7, 563.6, 1157.8]}, {"text": "Supply was considered the primary beneficiary that consolidates", "bbox": [71.3, 1158.7, 614.1, 1181.8]}, {"text": "this variable interest entity.", "bbox": [71.3, 1182.7, 303.6, 1205.8]}, {"text": "The lease financing, which includes $437 million of \"Long-term", "bbox": [71.3, 1230.6, 613.4, 1253.7]}, {"text": "Debt\" and $18 million of \"Noncontrolling Interests,\" at", "bbox": [71.3, 1254.6, 536.3, 1277.7]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009, is secured by, among other things, the", "bbox": [71.3, 1278.5, 566.9, 1301.6]}, {"text": "generation facility.  The debt matures at the end of the lease.  At", "bbox": [71.3, 1302.5, 611.9, 1325.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2009 and 2008, the facility, which was included in", "bbox": [71.3, 1326.4, 620.1, 1349.5]}, {"text": "\"Property, Plant and Equipment\" and \"Other intangibles\" on the", "bbox": [71.3, 1350.4, 609.0, 1373.5]}, {"text": "Balance Sheets, had a carrying value of $435 million and $441", "bbox": [71.3, 1374.4, 600.4, 1397.5]}, {"text": "million, net of accumulated depreciation and amortization of $48", "bbox": [71.3, 1398.3, 619.0, 1421.4]}, {"text": "million and $51 million.", "bbox": [71.3, 1422.3, 279.2, 1445.4]}, {"text": "4. Earnings Per Share", "bbox": [652.8, 104.9, 888.4, 128.2]}, {"text": "(PPL)", "bbox": [652.8, 152.9, 708.7, 176.1]}, {"text": "The basic and diluted EPS computations and reconciliations of", "bbox": [652.8, 200.8, 1181.5, 224.0]}, {"text": "the amounts of income and shares (in thousands) of common", "bbox": [652.8, 224.9, 1165.7, 248.0]}, {"text": "stock used in the calculations are:", "bbox": [652.8, 248.7, 938.8, 271.9]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [953.1, 296.7, 990.8, 315.1]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [1038.3, 296.7, 1076.0, 315.1]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [1125.3, 296.7, 1163.0, 315.1]}, {"text": "Income (Numerator)", "bbox": [652.8, 316.8, 804.6, 335.2]}, {"text": "Income from continuing operations after", "bbox": [652.8, 335.5, 927.4, 354.0]}, {"text": "income taxes attributable to PPL", "bbox": [660.3, 354.8, 881.8, 373.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [928.5, 354.7, 941.2, 373.1]}, {"text": "447 $", "bbox": [974.6, 354.7, 1024.7, 373.1]}, {"text": "907", "bbox": [1059.7, 354.7, 1084.8, 373.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1103.7, 354.7, 1112.0, 373.1]}, {"text": "1,001", "bbox": [1135.8, 354.7, 1173.4, 373.1]}, {"text": "Less amounts allocated to participating", "bbox": [652.8, 373.9, 918.2, 392.3]}, {"text": "securities", "bbox": [660.3, 393.0, 727.4, 411.5]}, {"text": "2", "bbox": [991.5, 393.0, 1004.0, 411.5]}, {"text": "5", "bbox": [1076.5, 393.0, 1084.8, 4